#. Tag: para
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter you will learn how to use the keyboard effectively, because "
"most operations can be done more quickly by keyboard than with the mouse. It "
"will take some time to learn the <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Key-"
"Bindings</link>, but mastering them saves you a lot of time. Please note "
"that &krusader; can use <link linkend=\"configure-shortcuts\">Key-binding "
"Profiles</link> to swap easily to other Key-binding setups, &eg; of other "
"commanders, or you can create your own key-bindings."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju se boste naučili učinkovito uporabljati tipkovnico, saj je "
"večino operacij s tipkovnico mogoče izvesti hitreje kot z miško. Trajalo bo "
"nekaj časa, da se naučite <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">vezav tipk</link>, "
"vendar vam njihovo obvladovanje prihrani veliko časa. Upoštevajte, da "
"&krusader; lahko uporablja <link linkend=\"configure-shortcuts\">profile za "
"vezavo tipk</link> za enostavno zamenjavo na druge nastavitve vezave tipk, "
"&eg; drugih poveljnikov ali pa ustvarite lastne vezave tipk."

#. Tag: para
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After starting &krusader;, the keyboard action can begin. Use <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to jump to the <link "
"linkend=\"list_panel\">Location Toolbar</link> where you can type the "
"desired folder. After <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Down;</keycombo> you "
"are in the <link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> and you can "
"type any command you desire, provided that the <link linkend=\"konfig-startup"
"\">terminal is shown</link>. Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Up;</"
"keycombo> to jump back to the active panel. If you want to jump to a file or "
"folder that starts with <literal>f</literal>, then simply press <keycap>f</"
"keycap> on the keyboard to use the <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">search bar</"
"link>. Use the &Enter; key to execute the file or to open a folder that has "
"the focus. Be sure to remember the Function Keys - <keycap>F3</keycap> to "
"View, <keycap>F4</keycap> to Edit, <keycap>F5</keycap> to Copy, <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> to Unpack, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Po zagonu &krusader; se lahko začne dejanje s tipkovnico. Uporabite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> za skok na "
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">lokacijsko orodno vrstico</link>, kjer lahko "
"vnesete želeno mapo. Po <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Down;</keycombo> "
"ste v <link linkend=\"termemu\">terminalskem emulatorju</link> in lahko "
"vnesete poljuben ukaz pod pogojem, da <link linkend=\"konfig-startup"
"\">prikazan je terminal</link>. Za skok nazaj na aktivno ploščo uporabite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Up;</keycombo>. Če želite skočiti na "
"datoteko ali mapo, ki se začne z <literal>f</literal>, preprosto pritisnite "
"<keycap>f</keycap> na tipkovnici, da uporabite <link linkend=\"quicksearch"
"\">iskalno vrstico</link>. Uporabite &Enter; tipko za izvedbo datoteke ali "
"za odpiranje mape, ki ima fokus. Ne pozabite si zapomniti funkcijskih tipk - "
"<keycap>F3</keycap> za ogled, <keycap>F4</keycap> za urejanje, <keycap>F5</"
"keycap> za kopiranje, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>U</"
"keycap></keycombo> za razpakiranje &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also perform several operations with the <link linkend=\"folder-tabs"
"\">Folder tabs</link>, including several <link linkend=\"edit-menu"
"\">selection</link> operations. And at the end you can close &krusader; with "
"<keycap>F10</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Izvedete lahko tudi več operacij z <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">zavihki "
"map</link>, vključno z več operacijami <link linkend=\"edit-menu"
"\">izbiranja</link>. In na koncu lahko zaprete &krusader; s <keycap>F10</"
"keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Key-Bindings</title>"
msgstr "<title>Veze tipk</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Key-Bindings</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Veze tipk</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the key-bindings (shortcuts) are configurable in the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu, if you like to use other key-bindings then "
"the default ones. You can even configure more actions to a Key-Binding (for "
"the actions that do not have a key-binding set by default). Please note that "
"some key-bindings are not &krusader; key-bindings (&eg; &plasma; key-"
"bindings). The key-bindings that &krusader; uses by default are listed below."
msgstr ""
"Večino povezav tipk (bližnjic) je mogoče konfigurirati v meniju <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, če želite uporabiti druge tipke- vezave nato "
"privzete. Konfigurirate lahko celo več dejanj za vezavo tipk (za dejanja, ki "
"nimajo privzeto nastavljene vezave tipk). Upoštevajte, da nekatere vezave "
"tipk niso &krusader; vezave tipk (&eg; &plasma; vezave tipk). Povezave tipk, "
"ki jih &krusader; privzete uporabe so navedene spodaj."

